content: RT @andypuzderThe jobs numbers keep dropping & by a lot. BLS revised June’s initial number down 43% & July 22% - so far. If the Fed wants insight on how dismal the Biden- Harris labor market is, best look at June’s and July’s numbers because the numbers for August are very likely overstated!
